Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person

  • public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    This Person class is constructed with StringBuffer class which is a MUTABLE class. //Because it is MUTABLE, we need to DEEP COPY the instance variables for the accessor methods. //the standard String class, is IMMUTABLE, which cannot be changed so the shallow is acceptable.
    Version:
    v1.1.1
    Author:
    - Matthew Dowell
